main event: A report from Tinker AFB describes a UFO sighting on 16 September 1952.
interesting points: The object was described as having a circular shape and moved back and forth., The sighting lasted approximately 45 minutes., Only one object was observed during the encounter., The course of the object was unknown, leading to speculation., The report includes reliable observer accounts from the area.
witness description: an observer at the 33rd Air Division, Tinker AFB
